Add support for non-debian distros (CentOS)

Use BASH_SOURCE instead of $0 (@see http://mywiki.wooledge.org/BashFAQ/028)

Docker security best practices (https://www.ernw.de/download/ERNW_Stocard_Docker-Devops-Security_fbarth-mluft.pdf)

- namespaces
- non root containers
- seccomp
- drop capabilities

Clustering: Docker Swarm, consul, Zookeeper...

